name: Fit-city-project
tagline: A project for the Introduction to Web Development Course
body:
### Fit City Project.
This was my first attempt at experimenting with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript and at creating a website. It was done to fulfill specific requirements assigned by my Introduction to Web Development professor at college.
This project was made by myself - Basma Amin- and my partner Sara Shams.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
